---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="Honest reviews and comparisons of web hosting, SaaS tools, and software." />
    <title>iRecommendU — Honest Tech Recommendations</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body>

    <!-- NAV -->
    <nav>
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <a href="/" class="logo">i<span>Recommend</span>U</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="/reviews">Reviews</a>
          <a href="/compare">Compare</a>
          <a href="/best-of">Best Of</a>
          <a href="/about">About</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="badge">Honest tech recommendations</div>
      <h1>Find the right tools,<br />without the guesswork</h1>
      <p>In-depth reviews and comparisons of web hosting, SaaS tools, and software — so you can make smarter decisions.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- CARDS -->
    <section class="cards-section">
      <div class="cards-grid">

        <div class="card">
          <span class="card-tag">Review</span>
          <h3>Hostinger 2026 Review</h3>
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>Is Hostinger still the best budget hosting? We tested speed, uptime, and support so you don't have to.</p>
          <a href="/reviews/hostinger" class="card-link">Read review →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card featured">
          <span class="card-tag">Compare</span>
          <h3>Bluehost vs Hostinger</h3>
          <div class="stars">★★★★☆</div>
          <p>Which hosting wins on price, speed, and ease of use for beginners in 2026?</p>
          <a href="/compare/bluehost-vs-hostinger" class="card-link">See comparison →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <span class="card-tag">Best Of</span>
          <h3>Best SaaS Tools 2026</h3>
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>Top picks for productivity, ecommerce, and marketing — tested and ranked by our team.</p>
          <a href="/best-of/saas-tools" class="card-link">View list →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- COMPARE BAR -->
    <section class="compare-bar">
      <p class="compare-label">Popular comparisons</p>
      <div class="compare-pills">
        <a href="/compare/shopify-vs-woocommerce" class="pill">Shopify vs WooCommerce</a>
        <a href="/compare/hostinger-vs-bluehost" class="pill">Hostinger vs Bluehost</a>
        <a href="/compare/notion-vs-obsidian" class="pill">Notion vs Obsidian</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer>
      <p>© 2026 iRecommendU · <a href="/disclaimer">Affiliate Disclosure</a> · All recommendations are independently tested</p>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>

<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: #f9f9f7;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e4;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }
  .nav-inner {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    height: 60px;
  }
  .logo {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }
  .logo span { color: #2563eb; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; }
  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #555;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: #1a1a1a; }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 64px 24px 48px;
    background: #ffffff;
  }
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #eff6ff;
    color: #1d4ed8;
    font-size: 12px;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #111;
  }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #555;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* CARDS */
  .cards-section {
    padding: 40px 24px;
    background: #f9f9f7;
  }
  .cards-grid {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e8e8e4;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .card.featured { border: 2px solid #93c5fd; }
  .card-tag {
    font-size: 11px;
    background: #eff6ff;
    color: #1d4ed8;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .card h3 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: #111;
  }
  .stars {
    color: #f59e0b;
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .card-link {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #2563eb;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .card-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  /* COMPARE BAR */
  .compare-bar {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e4;
    padding: 20px 24px;
  }
  .compare-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .compare-pills {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .pill {
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 7px 16px;
    border: 1px solid #e8e8e4;
    border-radius: 20px;
    color: #333;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: #f9f9f7;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .pill:hover { border-color: #2563eb; color: #2563eb; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 24px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #999;
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e4;
  }
  footer a { color: #999; text-decoration: underline; }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 26px; }
    .nav-links { gap: 16px; }
  }
</style>